result.name: REDUCING PREMATURE CORONARY ARTERY DISEASE IN MALAYSIA BY EARLY IDENTIFICATION OF FAMILIAL HYPERCHOLESTEROLAEMIA
result.description: A joint project between Universiti Teknologi MARA and The University of Nottingham to investigate the genetic landscape of familial hypercholesterolaemia (FH) in Malaysian primary care clinics, and detection rate of FH using different diagnostic criteria.
